entry.title: Install Telegram On Kali Linux
entry.summary: Install Telegram the Old School Way Head over to the official Telegram website and download the tar archive. Once it’s done, open up a terminal and navigate to the download directory. Then extract the tar archive. tar xvf tsetup*.tar.xz There’ll be a new directory named Telegram and there are two executable files in it: Telegram and Updater.
